20 October 2019: Once Liverpool scored a goal at Old Trafford, Man United refuses to let Liverpool score another goal and they also scored a goal to stop both of them from winning the game!
---
19 January 2020: Irritated from what happened 3 months ago, Liverpool scored 2 goals through their best players Virgil Van Dijk and Mo Salah at Anfield! If it was not for the VAR, Liverpool FC could've had scored 13 goals or more (in an attempt to make Man United unlucky at Anfield, which can also serve as a sweet revenge for their refusal to let Liverpool score yet another win at Old Trafford, 3 months ago)!
---
"YOU'LL NEVER WALK ALONE"!
